text: Joaquín Larraín (born 31 December 1953) is a Chilean equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Chile Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
